       <HR>
       <FONT size="+1">Modified chloroquines with single ring moiety or fused ring moiety
</FONT><BR>
       <BR><CENTER><b>Abstract</b></CENTER>
       <p> The disclosure provides modified <B><I>chloroquine</I></B> compounds having single ring
     or fused ring moieties. Also provided are pharmaceutical compositions
     comprising such compounds, methods of using such compounds to inhibit or
     treat diseases or conditions caused by <B><I>chloroquine</I></B>-resistant (CQ.sup.R)
     and <B><I>chloroquine</I></B>-sensitive (Cq.sup.S) malaria parasites and other
     CQ-susceptible microorganisms, and processes and intermediates useful for
     preparing such compounds.
</p>
       <HR>
