administered will depend on the subject being treated, the severity of the affliction, and the manner of administration, and is known to those skilled in the art.  Within these bounds, the formulation to be administered will contain a quantity of the
extracts or compounds disclosed herein in an amount effective to achieve the desired effect in the subject being treated.
