7-chloro-N-(3-(4-(pyridin-2- 2.7 4.8 9.5 yl)piperazin-1-yl)propyl)quinolin- 4-amine 7-chloro-N-(3-(4-(4- 0.14 0.8 0.3 fluorophenyl)piperazin-1- yl)propyl)quinolin-4-amine 7-chloro-N-(3-(4-(4- 0.1 0.48 0.3 methoxyphenyl)piperazin-1-
